latestPosts.caption:
Duniya jahan ki chizon par likhna itna aasan hai, Par kyun apni maa par hi likhna itna kathin hai....
Kya likhun aapke baare mein maa.....
Main toh khud aapki likhawat hun....
Aapne toh tab se pyaar lutaya hai ...
Jab aapne muje dekha bhi nahi tha....
Woh mera dukh, mere bin bataye samajh jaati hai....
Mere dil ka haal, mere chehre se padh leti hai.
Mere zakhmon ko bharna, usse bakhubhi aata hai....
Dawa kaam na aaye, toh nazar utarkar meri balayein lena,
Usse ache se aata hai.....
Meri har mushkil mein, woh meri dhaal ban jaati hai....
Khud se pehle har baar mujhe rakhti hai....
Woh meri aawaj se mera gham pehchan leti hai....
Meri sooji aankhon ka Kaaran, Rona hai, Ya kam Sona, woh dekh ke hi Bata deti hai...
Meri Khushiyon ke liye woh bhagwaan se bhi lad jaati hai...
Mujhe dard mein dekh, woh mujse jyaada roti hai...
Kam padne par woh apni thali tak ka niwala muje khilati hai...
Aise hi nahi maa, bhagwaan ka darja paati hai...
Kaise bataun aapko maa, ki aapke hone se hi mera hona hai...
Bina aapke toh mere liye ye jahan bhi suuna hai...
Jhukte honge logon ke sar madiron mein maa, Muje toh aap mein hi bhagwaan nazar aata hai...
Mera toh har din bhagwaan se bs yahi maangna hai...
Ki muje har Janam mein aap ki hi beti banna hai... ❤️🫂💎
Happy Mother’s Day Maa❤️😘😍 @archana_tiwari2 
.
